## 3. Can Cu Doi Chieu

Khi review module moi, doi chieu voi cac convention hien co:

- `tests/`: spec/test entry point, chi nen doc nhu kich ban test.
- `steps/`: dieu phoi flow nghiep vu hoac cac buoc test co the tai su dung.
- `components/pages/`: Page Object, thao tac page-level.
- `components/sections/`: UI section/component duoc tai su dung.
- `components/helpers/`: helper thao tac browser/element/dialog/navigation o muc thap.
- `components/assertions/`: assertion dung chung.
- `fixtures/`: fixture Playwright hoac setup state dung lai.
- `constants/`: selector, test id, message, timeout, route, endpoint path, status code, regex dung chung.
- `test-data/json/`: data test dang JSON.
- `test-data/files/`: file upload/download fixture.
- `test-data/env/.env.example`: bien moi truong mau, khong chua secret that.
- `types/`: type/interface dung chung cho payload, response, data model.
- `utils/`: utility khong phu thuoc truc tiep vao UI flow.
- `config/`: cau hinh project, env, timeout, browser/project mapping.

Neu code moi khong khop folder, de xuat folder dung va ly do ngan gon.

