## 4. Checklist Review Chinh

### A. Pham vi va anh huong

- Module moi co nam dung pham vi nguoi dung yeu cau khong?
- Co sua lan sang file khong lien quan khong?
- Co lam thay doi behavior cua flow cu ma khong co ly do/test khong?
- Ten file/module/class/function co noi dung ro rang va khop convention hien tai khong?

### B. Tach module va tinh tai su dung

- Spec co bi chua qua nhieu UI logic khong? Neu co, de xuat dua vao `steps/` hoac `components/pages/`.
- Page Object co qua dai hoac gom nhieu section khac nhau khong? Neu co, de xuat tach sang `components/sections/`.
- Helper moi co dung chung that su khong, hay chi dung cho mot flow? Neu chi dung mot flow, nen de gan flow/page do.
- Logic lap lai 2+ noi co nen tach thanh function/helper/constants khong?
- Function moi co lam mot viec ro rang khong, hay gom nhieu responsibility?
- Module co export/import gon khong, tranh import vong hoac import tu path sau bat on dinh?

### C. Dung folder va dung lop trach nhiem

- `tests/` chi dieu phoi test va assertion chinh, khong nen chua selector/loop thao tac dai.
- `steps/` chi dieu phoi flow, khong nen chua selector chi tiet lap lai nhieu.
- `components/pages/` chua thao tac UI cua mot page, khong nen chua data/env/config.
- `components/helpers/` chua helper thap, khong nen biet business flow qua nhieu.
- `constants/` chua gia tri dung lai, khong nen chua logic.
- `test-data/` chua data, khong nen chua secret that.

### D. Hardcode va flaky risk

Can canh bao neu code moi co:

- `page.waitForTimeout(...)`, `sleep(...)`, `setTimeout(...)` de cho UI/network.
- Timeout number lap lai truc tiep trong nhieu file.
- URL, credential, token, email/password that hardcode.
- Selector fragile: `nth-child`, dynamic class, CSS qua dai, text qua de thay doi.
- Test data tinh co the conflict khi chay parallel: email, orderId, username, filename.
- `test.only`, debug `page.pause()`, `console.log` tam thoi.
- Missing `await` voi Playwright action/assertion.
- `catch {}` rong hoac nuot loi.
- `force: true` hoac timeout tang cao ma khong co ly do.

Huong sua uu tien:
- Cho theo condition: locator/assertion/response/url/load state phu hop.
- Dua timeout dung chung vao `constants/` neu that su can.
- Dung env/config/test-data thay vi hardcode.
- Dung selector on dinh: role, label, test id, hoac constant selector da co.

### E. Test va verification

- Module moi co assertion du ro khong?
- Neu them helper/page/step moi, co test/spec goi den no khong?
- Neu them env/config moi, da cap nhat `.env.example` hoac README lien quan chua?
- Neu them command/script moi, da cap nhat README/rule huong dan chua?
- Co can chay `npm run typecheck`, `npm run test:list`, hoac test file lien quan khong?

### F. Data format moi dua vao project

Khi module moi them JSON/data fixture/payload mau, can kiem tra:

- Data co nam dung folder khong: JSON fixture vao `test-data/json/`, file upload/download vao `test-data/files/`, env sample vao `test-data/env/.env.example`.
- Data co dung format hop le khong: JSON parse duoc, field name nhat quan, khong tron nhieu kieu dat ten nhu `snake_case` va `camelCase` neu project da co convention.
- Data co chua secret, token, password that, email ca nhan, endpoint production that khong.
- Data co qua hardcode cho mot moi truong khong. Gia tri phu thuoc moi truong nen dua vao env/config.
- Data co lap lai nhieu noi khong. Neu lap lai, de xuat tao factory/helper hoac constants.
- Data co nguy co conflict khi chay parallel khong: email, username, orderId, filename, phone, ma don hang.
- Data co type/interface tuong ung khong neu duoc dung nhieu noi hoac payload phuc tap.
- Data co ro y nghia test khong: ten object/fixture phai noi duoc case dang cover, tranh `data1`, `test.json`, `abc.json`.

Huong sua uu tien:
- Tao file data rieng theo feature: `test-data/json/<feature>/<case-name>.json` neu data lon hoac co nhieu case.
- Tao helper/factory neu can sinh data unique theo test run.
- Tao type trong `types/` neu payload/response duoc dung lai.
- Cap nhat README lien quan neu them format data moi ma nguoi khac can biet cach dung.

### G. API format moi dua vao project

Khi module moi them API helper, request payload, mock response, route intercept, hoac API assertion, can kiem tra:

- Endpoint/path co bi hardcode lap lai khong. Endpoint dung lai nen dua vao constants/config.
- Base URL co lay tu env/config khong, khong hardcode domain staging/production trong code.
- Request payload co type/interface ro rang khong neu dung lai hoac phuc tap.
- Response/mock co dung schema mong doi khong: status code, content type, required fields, error format.
- API helper co tach dung trach nhiem khong: helper chi goi API/parse response, khong nen gom UI flow vao cung mot ham.
- Co validate `response.ok()`/status code truoc khi doc body khong.
- Co handle error ro rang khong, khong `catch {}` rong hoac tra ve `null` lam an loi.
- Co dung timeout/retry tuy tien khong. Khong them retry thu cong neu chua co ly do ro.
- Mock API co chi mock dependency phu khong, khong mock chinh API dang duoc test neu muc tieu la E2E flow.
- API data co isolated khi chay parallel khong, co cleanup neu tao record that khong.
- Ten file/folder API co ro domain khong, vi du `utils/order-api.ts`, `fixtures/api/order.fixture.ts`, `types/order-api.types.ts`.

Huong sua uu tien:
- Dua endpoint dung lai vao `constants/` hoac config phu hop.
- Tao type trong `types/` cho request/response phuc tap.
- Tao API helper rieng neu cung request duoc goi 2+ noi.
- Dung `request` fixture cua Playwright cho setup/teardown API trong test.
- Neu mock response, de fixture mock trong `test-data/json/` va dat ten theo case.

