## 5. Muc Do Nghiem Trong

### Critical - phai sua truoc merge

- Code moi lam test flaky ro rang: hardcoded wait, missing await, selector cuc ky bat on.
- Hardcode secret/token/password/URL moi truong that.
- `test.only`, `page.pause()`, debug code bi commit.
- Module moi dat sai lop trach nhiem lam flow kho maintain nghiem trong.
- Import/export lam runtime fail hoac tao circular dependency.
- Code moi thay doi behavior cua flow cu ma khong co test/ly do.
- API payload/response mock sai format lam test pass gia hoac fail runtime.
- Data fixture chua secret that hoac data production.

### Warning - nen sua trong PR nay

- Duplication 2+ noi nen tach helper/constants.
- Function qua dai, lam nhieu viec, ten khong ro.
- Page Object/step moi co dau hieu phinh to nhung chua gay loi ngay.
- Timeout/hardcode data khong phai secret nhung nen dua vao config/constants.
- Thieu assertion cu the, chi check visible chung chung.
- Data/API payload phuc tap nhung chua co type/interface.
- Endpoint/status/message lap lai nhieu noi nhung chua dua vao constants.

### Suggestion - co the cai thien

- Dat ten ro hon.
- Them `test.step()` de report de doc.
- Sap xep import/export gon hon.
- Bo sung comment ngan cho logic phuc tap.
- De xuat tach module sau nay neu reuse tang len.
- Dat lai ten fixture/mock response de noi ro case test.

