## 6. Cach Review Khi Thieu Thong Tin

Neu khong co diff:
- Hoi nguoi dung cung cap file/folder/module can review, hoac dung danh sach file ma nguoi dung chi dinh.
- Khong tu review toan project.

Neu chi co file moi:
- Review file do va cac file import truc tiep can thiet.
- Neu can check convention folder, chi doc README/rule/folder lien quan.

Neu phat hien loi nam o file cu:
- Chi neu ra neu loi do anh huong truc tiep den module moi.
- Ghi ro day la dependency risk, khong phai review toan project.

