## 7. Output Format Bat Buoc

### Tong quan

- Module duoc review: `[ten file/folder/module]`
- Pham vi: chi review code moi/theo diff, khong review toan project.
- Ket luan: `Can sua truoc merge` / `OK voi minor fix` / `Good to go`

| Muc do | So luong |
|---|---:|
| Critical | X |
| Warning | Y |
| Suggestion | Z |

### Issues

Voi moi issue, ghi theo format:

`[file:line] [Critical|Warning|Suggestion] Ten van de`

- Van de: mo ta ngan gon.
- Vi sao quan trong: impact voi maintainability/flaky/reuse/project convention.
- De xuat sua: dua huong sua hoac snippet ngan neu can.

### Module Structure Notes

Chi ghi khi co nhan xet ve folder/tach module/reuse.

- Dung folder chua?
- Co nen tach them khong?
- Co ham/helper/constants nao nen dung lai khong?
- Data/API format co nen tach sang `test-data/json/`, `types/`, `constants/` hoac API helper rieng khong?

### Can xac nhan

Chi dung khi khong chac:

- `[file:line]` cau hoi can nguoi viet xac nhan.

### Top viec can lam

Neu co issue, liet ke toi da 3 viec uu tien nhat.

