## 8. Nguyen Tac Cuoi

- Review ngan gon, tap trung vao code moi.
- Khong bien review module thanh audit toan he thong.
- Khong yeu cau refactor lon neu module moi van co the sua gon trong pham vi PR.
- Uu tien de xuat dung convention san co cua project hon la tao pattern moi.
- Moi feedback phai co gia tri hanh dong: neu khong chi ra duoc nen sua gi, khong nen ghi thanh issue.
